            "display_dots": false,
            "author_1": "Dr. Sarah Whitfield, PhD – Integrative Health Researcher [stars]",
            "image_1": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ChatGPT_Image_Oct_7_2025_02_26_11_AM.png",
            "text_1": "<p>\"PEA is one of the most well-researched comfort molecules available today. What sets Romira apart is the <strong>micronized format<\/strong> — this is what the clinical trials use, and it genuinely matters for <strong>absorption and results<\/strong>.\"<\/p>",
            "author_2": "Linda M. | Age: 54 [stars]",
            "image_2": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gempages_587632787746456096-33fca131-f4a3-4c51-a099-d0ff00d27fa6.png",
            "text_2": "<p>\"I've had nerve discomfort in my legs for years. After <strong>about three weeks<\/strong> on Romira PEA, that constant <strong>background irritation started to calm down<\/strong>. By week six I genuinely felt like myself again.\"<\/p>",
            "author_3": "Mark L. | Age: 50 [stars]",
            "image_3": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_design_22.png",
            "text_3": "<p>\"I tried CBD, I tried turmeric — nothing really stuck. This is different. It's <strong>gentler, cleaner<\/strong>, and it actually <strong>keeps working the longer you take it<\/strong>. On my third bottle now.\"<\/p>",
            "margin_top": 12,
            "margin_bottom": 24
          }
        },
