        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Science Behind It",
            "heading_size": "large",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>PEA — Palmitoylethanolamide — is a fatty acid compound your body already produces naturally when tissues come under stress or irritation. It is not a foreign molecule. Your body knows it, recognizes it, and uses it as part of its own protective response.<\/p><p>The mechanism is well-studied: PEA activates <strong>PPAR-alpha receptors<\/strong>, which help dial down the inflammatory signalling that keeps discomfort switched on. It also <strong>stabilizes mast cells<\/strong> — the cells responsible for nerve hypersensitivity — and supports healthy microglial regulation in the nervous system. In plain terms: PEA helps calm the internal overreaction that can show up as everyday pain, stiffness, and nerve-like irritation.<\/p><p>A <strong>2025 systematic review identified 47 randomized controlled trials<\/strong> across multiple patient populations — the strongest clinical evidence base of any comfort-support ingredient in its class. A <strong>2024 meta-analysis<\/strong> found that benefits continue to improve beyond 30 days, with a <strong>35.1% reduction in pain intensity in the first month<\/strong> and a <strong>further 35.4% reduction in the second month<\/strong>.<\/p><p>This is why PEA is not an instant fix. It is a daily-use, cumulative-support molecule — and why we built our product and guarantee around a full 60-day protocol.<\/p><p>Romira uses <strong>99% pure micronized Palmitoylethanolamide<\/strong> — the same particle size and format used in clinical research — because micronization directly improves absorption and effectiveness.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_LPNzCP": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is It Safe?",
            "heading_size": "large",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes. PEA is one of the most thoroughly studied comfort-support ingredients available. In oral use, PEA is generally described as <strong>well tolerated<\/strong> across clinical populations — including older adults and people with chronic conditions.<\/p><p>Romira PEA is <strong>100% natural, non-GMO, vegan<\/strong>, and made without artificial fillers, binders, or preservatives. Every batch is <strong>third-party tested for purity and potency<\/strong> and produced in a <strong>GMP-certified facility in the USA<\/strong>.<\/p><p><strong>Free from:<\/strong> Gluten, Soy, Eggs, Dairy, Nuts, Preservatives, and Animal Products.<\/p><p>The most commonly noted side effect in clinical literature is mild nausea in some users — usually resolved by taking capsules with food. If you are pregnant, nursing, or currently taking prescription medication, please consult your doctor before use.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_ccfrML": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients",
            "heading_size": "large",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Each daily serving (2 veggie capsules) contains:<\/p><p><strong>600mg Palmitoylethanolamide (PEA)<\/strong><br\/>99% pure, micronized for superior bioavailability. The clinically evidenced dose for comfort and nerve support.<\/p><p><strong>Other Ingredients:<\/strong> Vegetable cellulose (capsule shell). Nothing else.<\/p><p><strong>Free from:<\/strong> Gluten, Soy, Eggs, Dairy, Nuts, Preservatives, Animal Products<\/p><p><strong>Made in the USA<\/strong> — GMP Certified, Third-Party Lab Tested<\/p><p><strong>No fillers. No binders. No synthetic additives. Just pure PEA in the form your body actually uses.<\/strong><\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WVx44p": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "60-Day Guarantee",
            "heading_size": "large",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We offer a <strong>60-day money-back guarantee<\/strong> — because PEA works cumulatively, and we want you to have the full evaluation window the evidence recommends.<\/p><p>If for any reason you are not completely satisfied after completing your 60-day protocol, we will issue a <strong>full refund, no questions asked<\/strong>. Simply contact our support team and we will take care of you.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
