        "sub_heading_height": 150,
        "sub_heading_align": "left",
        "sub_heading_align_mobile": "center",
        "sub_heading_mt": 40,
        "sub_heading_position": "2",
        "sub_heading_position_mobile": "4",
        "text": "<p>✅ <strong>99% Pure Micronized PEA — The Form That Actually Works<\/strong><\/p><p>Most PEA products use standard or poorly specified grades. Romira uses 99% pure micronized Palmitoylethanolamide — the particle size used in clinical trials. Micronization improves surface area and absorption. This is not a marketing claim. It is what the research uses.<\/p><p>✅ <strong>600mg — The Clinically Evidenced Dose<\/strong><\/p><p>The most studied oral dose for PEA is 600mg daily. That is exactly what Romira delivers — not a reduced amount padded with fillers, not a proprietary blend that hides the real quantity. A clean, transparent 600mg per serving.<\/p><p>✅ <strong>Single Ingredient. Nothing Hidden.<\/strong><\/p><p>No blends, no fillers, no co-ingredients added to inflate the label. Just PEA. A single-ingredient formula keeps the claim story clean, the product traceable, and the dose meaningful.<\/p><p>✅ <strong>Built Around the 60-Day Protocol — Because the Evidence Demands It<\/strong><\/p><p>The 2024 meta-analysis showed PEA's benefits continue building from day 30 to day 60. Most brands sell 30-day bottles and encourage you to reorder. We built our product and our guarantee around the full 60-day evaluation window — because that is where the results are.<\/p>",
        "text_custom": false,
        "text_font": "josefin_sans_n4",
        "text_size": 18,
        "text_size_mobile": 18,
        "text_height": 150,
