        "sub_heading": "<h3>You have probably already tried things that did not work. You deserve a brand that takes the evidence seriously — and gives you the right dose, the right form, and the right expectations.<\/h3>",
        "sub_heading_custom": false,
        "sub_heading_font": "josefin_sans_n4",
