        "text": "<p>✅ <strong>Made in the USA — GMP Certified<\/strong><br\/>Every batch produced in a certified facility with full quality controls in place.<\/p><p>✅ <strong>Third-Party Lab Tested<\/strong><br\/>Independently verified for purity, potency, and consistency — no guessing what is actually in the capsule.<\/p><p>✅ <strong>99% Pure Micronized PEA<\/strong><br\/>The clinical grade. Not a cheaper, inferior form padded with fillers or hidden in a proprietary blend.<\/p><p>✅ <strong>60-Day Money-Back Guarantee<\/strong><br\/>Built around the evidence. Give it 60 days — or your money back, no questions asked.<\/p>",
